data.description: One or more photo(s) has been virtually staged. Charming South Tampa Home - Must See! Welcome to this delightful 3-bedroom, 1-bathroom home in the heart of South Tampa! This charming  property boasts a host of modern features that make it a perfect place to call home. This well-maintained home offers peace of mind with a newer roof,  air conditioning system, and water heater, ensuring your comfort and reducing future maintenance costs. Enjoy the elegant blend of tile and hardwood  floors throughout, adding a touch of sophistication to each room. The kitchen is a true highlight, featuring new updates and stainless-steel appliances.  It's a chef's dream and perfect for entertaining. Situated on a large corner lot, this home offers privacy and room to roam. The fenced backyard  provides a secure space for kids to play and pets to explore. Plus, there's a relaxing patio where you can unwind after a long day. The open floor plan  creates a welcoming atmosphere, perfect for family gatherings and entertaining friends. This South Tampa gem won't last long! Schedule your showing  today and experience the warmth and charm this home has to offer. Don't miss out on this fantastic opportunity to make it your own. Contact me now  for more information!
